# metadataTypes

**Instance Property**

A set of key paths that represent metadata types that the data detection system identifies.

## Declaration

```swift
var metadataTypes: Set<PartialKeyPath<NSPasteboard.DetectedMetadata>> { get }
```

## Accessing metadata

- **contentType**: The content type of a file that the data detection system identifies when the pasteboard contains a file URL.
